OL,3,CRyanair to boost free cabin baggage
OL,4,Csize ahead of the summer holidays
OL,6,FThe change comes in response to an
OL,7,Fagreement made by European airlines to
OL,8,Fstandardise the dimensions across
OL,9,Fvarious air carriers.
OL,11,FRyanair's allowance increase is larger
OL,12,Fthan the newly announced European
OL,13,Fminimum luggage size of 40 x 30 x 15cm.
OL,15,FRyanair confirmed it would be making
OL,16,Fthose changes over the "coming weeks"
OL,17,Fahead of the summer holidays.
