OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the airline said:
OL,12,F"Ryanair's current free 'personal bag'
OL,13,Fsize is 40 x 25 x 20cm. Following the
OL,14,Fnew EU minimum bag size of 40 x 30 x
OL,15,F15cm, Ryanair will increase its max
OL,16,F'personal bag' dimensions to 40 x 30 x
OL,17,F20cm, so that Ryanair's 'personal bag'
OL,18,Fallowance is bigger than the EU
OL,19,Fstandard.
