OL,4,Csize ahead of the summer holidays
OL,6,F"This change will be implemented over
OL,7,Fthe coming weeks, as our airport bag
OL,8,Fsizers are adjusted."
OL,10,FThe trade body Airlines for Europe
OL,11,F(A4E) has been in talks with Adina
OL,12,FValean, the EU transport commissioner
OL,13,Fin Brussels, about simplifying air
OL,14,Ftravel for passengers.
OL,16,FIt said all A4E airlines "will roll
OL,17,Fout the guaranteed dimensions and have
OL,18,Fthem in place by the end of the 2025
OL,19,Fsummer season".
