OL,6,FA4E airlines include Ryanair, easyJet,
OL,7,FAir France-KLM and Lufthansa Group.
OL,9,FOurania Georgoutsakou, managing
OL,10,Fdirector of A4E, said: "This will
OL,11,Falign A4E members with the decision of
OL,12,Fmember states made last month and
OL,13,Fbring more clarity to passengers
OL,14,Facross Europe.
OL,16,F"From city-hoppers to family
OL,17,Ftravellers, everyone will benefit from
OL,18,Fthe same clear rule across our
OL,19,Fmembers' networks."
